    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so it's mostly about the contract terms. it just feels weird that this huge sum of money is just sitting there in a \"neutral\" vault or something while we wait. like, who is actually in charge of watching over it to make sure nothing goes wrong with the funds?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
